* An Account cannot be anonymized if it has an open Lead -  the Account field on Lead marks the association of Lead and Account, the Status of Lead is NOT Closed-Converted or Closed-Not Converted {color:#00875A}*- OK*{color}
* An Account cannot be anonymized if it has an open Opportunity connected - Stage field is NOT Closed-won or Closed -Lost {color:#00875A}*- OK*{color}
* An Account cannot be anonymized if in the pas 6 months there was a Lead or Opportunity created for that Account {color:#00875A}*- OK*{color}
* There is a new field on Account HasNoOpenLeadOpp, not accessible to users, that confirms if the anonymization can be done based on above criteria (if HasNoOpenLeadOpp = FALSE  the Account cannot be anonymized) {color:#00875A}*- OK*{color}
